VN Boards
[[Image:Vnboards ss.png|thumb|right]] '''VN Boards''' is a giant message board site with boards for every [[MMORPG]] in existence.

After taking three seconds to consider this, it's not surprising that the VN is one of the filthiest [[shit|cesspools]] on the [[Internets]].  Along with [[MySpace]], the fact that no vengeful comet has yet fallen out of the sky to vaporize the VN's data center is proof that there is a [[God]], and he hates us.  There is a particular user there: Dark_EternalFF who happens to have the worlds largest penis.

Most of the people who post on these boards are right-wing racists who hate browns, but would quickly use them for slavery.

The VNboards is apparently the place where the people involved with the infamous [[Cloudsong]] incident, with the enraged nerd claiming that [[unwarranted self-importance|he owns the VN boards]].

Balls balls balls balls balls balls balls.
